course.label: Trauma Informed Social Work with Children and Adolescents

sectionText: This section is for OUTREACH 2015 Cohort only.  This class combines an intensive weekend model (2 weekends, 8 hrs/day) of face to face meetings with online modules in Illinois Compass.  Face-to-face class will meet on the following Saturdays and Sundays: 2/18-19 and 4/1-4/2 from 9:00-5:00  in Room 2019 with time for lunch.
